Bible all around us: appearing in advertisments. Advantage of using Bible to sell things: it comes with built-in stories that people already know.

Tendency to separate religion and secular things, putting science, reason, and the Enlightenment under "secular" and faith, irrational, and Dark Ages under "religion"

Augstine literal != our literal

Dominion: ruling over. Control of. Absolute ownership. Use of. Unity with (hebrew word also used in marriage context)

See slides about dominion timeline and how the interpretation of this word has changed throughout history

Being at the centre of the universe wasn't really a good thing, so when galileo and copernicus challenged the geocentric view they were not "dethroning" humans, but "enthroning" humans as being above everything.


